She looked at Black Aracnia. "I'm doing Ok. I still can't walk yet." 
she looked at her legs and felt useless. "And I can't stop shaking. I 
don't know why either."  She tried to smile. "But other than that, I 
think I'm ok." She wanted to rip her body apart and fix it.  But she 
knew that was not possable.  If only she could stop shaking.
